snippet.title: Floyd of the Jungle Gameplay
snippet.description: Floyd of the Jungle on Atari 800 - released 1982.  Gameplay from one of the best multi-player games of all time!  You may laugh at that, but when you get 4 people racing for that voluptuous babe on each level (who remarkably resembles a gray oompa loompa - what with those protruding tumors on the sides of her thighs), it gets intense!  :)  Also, I never said I was good - consider yourself forewarned.
